headline: Blind Vendors Ohana Selects Square to Power Accessible, Multi-Location Retail Operations at Honolulu Airport
summary: HONOLULU, February 23, 2026--Today, Square announced that Pages & Pages, a retail business facilitated by Blind Vendors Ohana (BVO) with ten stores at the Daniel K. Inouye International Airport (HNL), has selected Square's commerce platform to power its operations.
